---
title: Seared Pork Steak & Almond Topping with Buttery Cannellini Beans & Garlicky Greens
description: You might not be able to plant a cannellini bean and have it sprout a giant bean stalk but it certainly feels magical when it’s buttered up
and alongside a slice of seared pork. The almond crunch topping though is the real mystical element of this dish. Maybe it is magic!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

